  "description": "This super quick breakfast is a variation of [Huevos rancheros en sombrero](/recipes/huevos-rancheros-en-sombrero) but doesn’t need [salsa de frijol](/recipes/salsa-de-frijol), refried beans, [charred red sauce](/recipes/charred-red-sauce) or [guacamole](/recipes/guacamole), so it’s a good option when you only have a piece of cheese and a jar of kimchi (or any other [pickle](/tags/pickling/)) in your fridge. A combination of melted cheese and kimchi makes it surprisingly hot and juicy — a perfect dish to wake you up in the morning.",
